				<td colspan="2"><span>Ive mainly grped with my bard for the past 44 lvls. Ive rarely soled at all, other then snare/fear.
<br />

<br />
Ive heard of a few ways to solo. One is chant kite. Whats that and can someone explain, in simple terms, how its done? Ive read the guides and I still have problems with it.
<br />

<br />
Another form is ae kite? How does this work? We only have 1 ae dot dont we?
<br />

<br />
The other is charm kite. This one ive never had luck with and have lots tons of exp due to deaths. I guess the idea is to charm a mob, and send him into 3 or 4 other mobs, then when low health, finish him off. Problem is the other mobs kill me.
<br />

<br />
Would be greatful for any tips =) Thanks</span></td>
