				<td colspan="2"><span>With a drum equipped and selo's running, NOTHING should catch you.  To kill your 'pet' after you break charm, twist in 2-3 dots in this order (At 44 I would twist Selo's, Chant of Flame, Chant of Disease and Fufil's if twisting 4 songs).  These songs have a range of 200 so nothing should be able to get close to you.
